Create Prebuilt View

acme nw -sb xe -dl polaris_dev -gl -wit -dir <view-name>

This will pull a prebuilt view using latest green label (-gl)
The view will be created under /witspace/ytse/
A symbolic link will also be placed in /nobackup/ytse/<view-name>


# Note: following commands should be run under /nobackup/ytse/

# My wit space
/witspace/ytse

# To check space
wit space list -space <space-name>

# To increase storage
wit space manage -space <space-name> -size "+100*1024"

# Detach and reattach (can be used to fix read-only problem)
wit space detach -space <space-name>
wit space attach -space <space-name>

# To delete workspace
wit space delete -space <space-name>

# To migrate changes to a newer label
wit space migrate -space <space-name> -branch <branch-name> -snapshot <label>

# To move over to a regular acme workspace
wit space delete -space <space-name> -archive
acme new -sb <sourcebase> -dl <orig-label> -dir <workspace> -checkpoint <checkpoint-id>

